=== EVENT_GHOST_SHIP ===
# id: 5
# title: Ghost Ship
# chinese_title: 幽灵船
# category: DistressSignal
# mode: starmap

A ship of ancient design drifts silently — no power signatures, no life signs. Its hull is covered in strange glyphs that seem to shift when you look away.

* [Board and investigate]
  ~ combat_reward(2, 20)
  调查 (diàochá) — investigate
* [Scan the hull glyphs from your ship]
  ~ gain_radical("鬼")
  符号 (fúhào) — glyph
* [Keep your distance — some things are best left alone]
  ~ nothing
  远离 (yuǎnlí) — stay away
